name: Employee Invoice
query:
SELECT
  `tabTimesheet`.employee_name as "Employee Name:Data:200",
  `tabTimesheet`.job_order_detail as "Job Order:Link/Job Order:200",
  `tabTimesheet`.company as "Company:Link/Company:200",
  `tabTimesheet`.total_billable_hours as "Hours Worked:Data:200",
  `tabTimesheet`.start_date as "Start Date:Date:200",
  `tabTimesheet`.end_date as "End Date:Date:200",
  `tabTimesheet`.total_billable_amount as "Total Paid:Data:200",
  `tabTimesheet`.non_satisfactory as "Unsatisfactory:Check:200" ,
  `tabTimesheet`.dnr as "DNR:Check:200" 
  
  
  
  
FROM `tabTimesheet`
WHERE `tabTimesheet`.start_date >= %(from_date)s and `tabTimesheet`.end_date <= %(to_date)s
